<h3 id="toc1"><span><span style="color:#6BAB30;"><em>Why?</em></span></span></h3>
<p>Beneath the ocean, in unexplored depths, there is a tragedy unfolding.</p>
<p>Desperate underwater beings have been stranded after the demise of their home, and to them, it seems to them like there is no hope. The only beacon of light they can enjoy is the high-wattage underwater spotlight set up by Manna, alongside similar setups by groups such as Global Occult and SCP, which has brought the only illumination to their otherwise dismal and dreary lives as underwater refugees.</p>
<p><em>Folks, please really try to sell the deprivation they're feeling down there. We want donors to be thinking of their neediness. Remember, these are for donors already ready to loosen the purse strings. We're working in degrees here. It's not a numbers game, so don't hold back. I know what you're capable of.</em><br />
- <em>Mark</em></p>
<h3 id="toc2"><span><span style="color:#6BAB30;"><em>When Can I Donate?</em></span></span></h3>
<ul>
<li>How can you donate? Send cash or check to your local branch affiliate or our downtown streetcorner criers.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: salmon">Am I awake? You can donate in dreams, thanks to a partnership between O.N.E.I Financial Dreampipe and Manna Financial Management LLC. Direct dream deposits accepted, please keep checkbooks on bedside table for sleep-banking reference.</span></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="toc3"><span><span style="color:#6BAB30;"><em>Who Hates Refugees?</em></span></span></h3>
<p>Jim Bread, currently a so-called candidate for City of 3 Portlands at-large Alderman, believes that Manna not &quot;doing enough to provide genuine support or benefit&quot; to those who Manna exists to salvage from despair.</p>
<p>NOTE THE FACT that Mr. Bread has been invited multiple times to sit with or even chair the Manna Charity Independent Citizen's Tribunate, to attend even one of our facilities, or to take any kind of an official tour. This criminal candidate resorts to trespassing and leaning on the wording of privacy laws to launch a smear campaign.</p>
<p>Jim Bread is a braggadocios liar who is also so incompetent he leaves his camera lens on all the time when trying to take &quot;incriminating&quot; photos of Manna's Pacific refugee facilities. Why will Jim go on official Coalition and Foundation group tours for those groups' refugee management facilities but not the ones sponsored by Manna? It's probably because they're all up to no good against us.</p>
<p><em>Not paranoid enough. Get into some of that online conspiracy stuff, it's like catnip to those dipsticks.</em> &#8212; <em>Mark</em></p>
</div>
