<p><span style="color: blue">Manna Financial Management LLC is 'managing' donations and through a few other layers of shell there's plenty of chances to nibble with fees until it's all gone, plus we have cash flow to grow, baby! No holding back because old man Alphonse wants us to hold everyone's hand. This is big time.</span></p>
