<div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div>
<div style="text-align:justify;">
<div style="opacity: 1"><em>Three Portlands</em> - Freshly minted leader of the 3Ports chapter of the Manna Charitable Foundation Mark Hanna Jr. abruptly resigned his post today, citing a need for the charity to move on from the scandal which has swirled around the embattled philanthropist ever since documents emerged showing him belittling donors and openly planning to embezzle money with unnamed co-conspirators.<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></div>
